    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1891-09-04T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1891-09-04T00:00:00-05:00" n="72"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d72">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Wharton</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Pacheco</persName>
                    </hi>.</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1891-09-04">
                            <hi rend="italic">September 4, 1891</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Mr. Wharton inquires as to the length of time for which, under the contract, the
                    Salvadorian Government claims it can detain the <hi rend="italic">City of
                        Panama</hi> and asks the meaning of the offer of indemnity for unlawful
                    detention if the vessel is not to be detained longer than the contract
                    permits.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
